channel.title: 718 help! cannot launch
channel.description: Hey guys, I don't know if this is a client issue or what- but I know what the problem is I just don't know how to resolve it. Whenever I launch my server, it runs perfectly fine, but on the client it says "Check for updates 1%" and stays there forever and says "j5_cannot_connect". Im pretty positive that it is the cache from the server, do I just drag it into the client folder?? im so confused with this and there are NO tutorials on even how to do this...
